v 3
d latinobarometro. Load, harmonize, and enrich Latinobarometro survey waves
d
d Downloads a Latinobarometro survey wave directly from latinobarometro.org,
d optionally harmonizes variable names with the official time-series crosswalk,
d and optionally constructs country-population-scaled weights for pooled analysis.
d
d Requires: Stata version 14 or later
d Optional dependency for addpopulation: wbopendata
d
d Author: Jorge Soler-Lopez, Bocconi University
d Support: jorge.solerlopez@phd.unibocconi.it
d Distribution-Date: 20260715
f latinobarometro.ado
f latinobarometro.sthlp
